{"tid":383679,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【借伯父上位】旅居日本評立法　國歌填詞人侄女稱深受感動","createTime":"2017-09-01T16:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T16:57:44.000Z","uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8e5bdf215b2924d31a6e42ea1ecd735a46c358","tid":383679,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會今日通過《中華人民共和國國歌法》，<span style=\"color: red;\">國歌《義勇軍進行曲》的填詞人田漢，其侄女田偉稱對立法非常感動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n田偉現旅居日本，早年於日本一直向外國宣揚國歌，並傳遞國歌內的中國力量。田偉更成立文化研究會、受邀演唱國歌，更自費出版《國歌80周年》書籍。今年7月，更於日本舉辦了「田漢&middot;聶耳的故事」音樂會，以國歌開場。<br />\n<br />\n田偉認為，《國歌法》鼓勵人民唱國歌，令她大受鼓舞，並稱會繼續為研究和傳唱國歌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170901/s00004/1504272596106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170901%2Fs00004%2F1504272596106&d=NL2wxML9PHmKuXjXFwwIKB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=b8cf4a95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170901%2Fs00004%2F1504272596106&h=856df774\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170901/s00004/1504272596106</a>"},{"pid":"149badd24e8d80f72140ecbf8ce12b528c2f1f77","tid":383679,"uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/01/Tianhan-350x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FTianhan-350x400.jpg&h=2893c94d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ec7a606200ced0b91a447f3155044fcd58fa57c","tid":383679,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/01/Tianhan-350x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%